name: INFINITE CHAOS | ISSUE 4/4
description:
a non-stop flow of random glyphs in a single, static colour; the intentional lack of variance makes for a striking contrast

do you possess the faculty required to stare down a force this bold, stark, and unyielding? can you handle being faced with such raw and unfettered chaos, straight from the universe itself while it sparks and connects itself directly to your core?

this is an open edition to celebrate 5k followers. remaining copies will be burnt in 36 hours, and the number of remaining editions will be used as an input variable in a future nft
